                                        <li><strong>Year 5:</strong> Reached our first million customers, marking a milestone in our mission to connect people and products.</li>
                                        <li><strong>Today:</strong> A trusted name in eCommerce, continuously evolving to meet the needs of our diverse audience.</li>
